sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Dev as Developer
    participant Git as Git Forge
    participant CI as CI Runner
    box Transparent Build Stages
        participant B as Builder
        participant T as Test Grid
        participant R as Registry
    end
    participant CD as CD Controller
    participant K as Kubernetes

    Dev->>Git: git push (feature branch)
    Git--)CI: webhook: push event

    CI->>+B: build image
    B->>B: restore cache + compile
    B-->>-CI: image:sha

    par Run test matrix
        CI->>T: unit tests
    and
        CI->>T: integration tests
    and
        CI->>T: e2e tests
    end

    break any test suite fails
        T-->>CI: ❌ failures
        CI--)Dev: notify: pipeline red
    end

    Note right of CI: All green —<br/>proceed to publish
    CI->>+R: push image:sha
    R-->>-CI: digest

    critical Promote to production
        CD->>+K: apply manifests (canary 10%)
        K-->>-CD: rollout started
    option Health checks fail
        CD->>K: rollback to previous
        CD--)Dev: notify: auto-rolled back
    option Manual approval timeout
        CD->>CD: hold at canary
    end

    opt Canary healthy for 10m
        CD->>K: scale to 100%
    end

    K--)Dev: deployment succeeded
